{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"献给您，敬爱的毛主席","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1952,"month":5,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给您，敬爱的毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民志愿军归国代表团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们见到了您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是无限的快乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不尽的欢欣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来自朝鲜的英雄阵地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烟火弥漫的战壕里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在冰天雪地的山岗上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大雨滂沱的树林里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们时刻都在向往您。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何暴力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都不能阻止我们无畏前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为有一个最伟大的领袖——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明的毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是光荣，就是胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您英明领导下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国变得更年青，更美丽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人表现了忘我劳动和无穷智慧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不断涌现的新纪录，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发射着光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民愉快地劳动在田野上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着“集体”“互助”的道路前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为爱国丰产而努力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年儿童们，都在："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻准备着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为实现您的伟大理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻炼身体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国各兄弟民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲密团结在您的旗帜下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快乐的生活在祖国的大家庭里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您提出的“三反”“五反”运动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变了旧社会的恶习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打垮了不法资产阶级分子的猖狂进攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奠定了祖国工业化的根基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………………………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………………………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从昆仑山巅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到黄河之源；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从南海之滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到鸭绿江畔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处歌唱胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处歌颂着您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——最敬爱的毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是您的好战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是英雄祖国的儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们赤诚的向您宣誓："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国的荣誉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了朝鲜人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为保卫世界和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定取得反侵略战争的最后胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军全体同志都关怀着您。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们托我们带来了一句话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候亲爱的毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国的人民都想念您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们托我们带来了一句话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候亲爱的毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都亲切地祝福您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万寿无疆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远健康！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们热烈地向您高呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁！万万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十三日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}